---
title: Crowd Codes - Promo Codes Without the Friction
description: Trouvez des codes promo qui marchent. Sans pubs, sans popups, sans friction. Codes visibles directement, triés par fraîcheur.
eleventyComputed:
  canonicalUrl: "{{ site.hostname }}/"
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block head %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebSite",
  "name": "Crowd Codes",
  "url": "{{ site.hostname }}/",
  "description": "Codes promo vérifiés, copiés en un clic. Sans pubs, sans inscription.",
  "potentialAction": {
    "@type": "SearchAction",
    "target": {
      "@type": "EntryPoint",
      "urlTemplate": "{{ site.hostname }}/?q={search_term_string}"
    },
    "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"
  }
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Organization",
  "name": "Crowd Codes",
  "url": "{{ site.hostname }}/",
  "description": "Codes promo vérifiés, copiés en un clic."
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<h1>Crowd Codes</h1>
<p>Codes promo sans friction.</p>

<search>
  <input
    type="search"
    id="search"
    class="search-input"
    placeholder="Rechercher une marque..."
    aria-label="Rechercher une marque"
    autofocus
  >
</search>

<section id="results" class="results-container" aria-label="Codes promo">
  <!-- Results populated by JS in Story 3.2 -->
</section>
{% endblock %}
